    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>指尖感受真实钓鱼操作！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平静水面之下，等待你的可不是普通鱼儿。紧张时刻拉起鱼线，那一瞬间的刺激感，让你亲身体验传说之鱼上钩的快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/f1d73ed446b23ead5ad3dc75d328c151.poster.avif?t=1772094029\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/f1d73ed446b23ead5ad3dc75d328c151.webm?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/f1d73ed446b23ead5ad3dc75d328c151.mp4?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超过100种稀有鱼类和传奇装备</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通的鱼已经不稀奇了？现在轮到真正的大物、白化猛兽、深海巨人登场！强化钓竿与鱼线轮，装备最强套装，钓起你的梦幻大鱼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/2e51c34fc05360930edf53ebcdbd00c1.poster.avif?t=1772094029\" width=800 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/2e51c34fc05360930edf53ebcdbd00c1.webm?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/2e51c34fc05360930edf53ebcdbd00c1.mp4?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>梦想之船开启全球钓鱼之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乘坐奢华游艇，出发前往世界各大海域！东南亚碧海、神秘印度洋、壮阔大西洋，以及南北美洲的黄金渔场—带你开启华丽的钓鱼冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/f82708cae2f210c8e317e646444ac2fd.poster.avif?t=1772094029\" width=616 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/f82708cae2f210c8e317e646444ac2fd.webm?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/f82708cae2f210c8e317e646444ac2fd.mp4?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富模式与个性记录</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 自由模式 — 适合享受独钓时光</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 个人赛 — 挑战全球钓鱼玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 对战出航 — 组队与对手较量</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与全球玩家一同竞技、合作，享受不断延伸的乐趣。钓获稀有鱼种收录图鉴，自由装饰你的专属水族馆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/a39d8992aabdc873c4eb5612462a843f.poster.avif?t=1772094029\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/a39d8992aabdc873c4eb5612462a843f.webm?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/a39d8992aabdc873c4eb5612462a843f.mp4?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>个性化时尚定制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钓鱼也能很时尚！自由搭配服饰和装备，打造属于你的独特风格。运动风、华丽风、搞笑风—这片海域，就是你的T台！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/e4d0d98a1c0db105efcb67f27d0648d0.poster.avif?t=1772094029\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128000/extras/e4d0d98a1c0db105efcb67f27d0648d0.webm?t=1772094029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
